\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:343px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"Tổng thống Mỹ Donald Trump (tr\u0026aacute;i) v\u0026agrave; Nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n Kim Jong-un. Ảnh: Kyodo/TTXVN\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"343\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eTổng thống Mỹ Donald Trump (tr\u0026aacute;i) v\u0026agrave; Nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n Kim Jong-un. Ảnh: Kyodo/TTXVN\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eQuan chức n\u0026agrave;y n\u0026ecirc;u r\u0026otilde;: “\u0026Ocirc;ng \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/donald-trump-tag673.epi\"\u003eTrump\u003c/a\u003e dĩ nhi\u0026ecirc;n từng b\u0026agrave;y tỏ sẵn s\u0026agrave;ng gặp lại \u0026ocirc;ng Kim Jong Un trong tương lai, nhưng cuộc gặp n\u0026agrave;y kh\u0026ocirc;ng nằm trong chương tr\u0026igrave;nh của chuyến đi lần n\u0026agrave;y”.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTrước đ\u0026oacute;, c\u0026ugrave;ng ng\u0026agrave;y, Bộ trưởng Thống nhất \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/han-quoc-tag2475.epi\"\u003eH\u0026agrave;n Quốc\u003c/a\u003e Chung Dong Young nhận định c\u0026oacute; khả năng hai nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo gặp nhau khi \u0026ocirc;ng Trump tới b\u0026aacute;n đảo Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n v\u0026agrave;o tuần tới. Tổng thống Trump dự kiến đến H\u0026agrave;n Quốc ng\u0026agrave;y 29/10 để dự Diễn đ\u0026agrave;n Hợp t\u0026aacute;c Kinh tế ch\u0026acirc;u \u0026Aacute; - Th\u0026aacute;i B\u0026igrave;nh Dương (APEC).\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo truyền th\u0026ocirc;ng \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/my-tag81.epi\"\u003eMỹ\u003c/a\u003e, c\u0026aacute;c quan chức trong ch\u0026iacute;nh quyền Tổng thống Trump đ\u0026atilde; thảo luận kh\u0026ocirc;ng ch\u0026iacute;nh thức về khả năng thu xếp cuộc gặp với nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n. Cuộc gặp gần nhất giữa hai nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo l\u0026agrave; năm 2019 trong nhiệm kỳ Tổng thống đầu ti\u0026ecirc;n của \u0026ocirc;ng Trump.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026Ocirc;ng Trump trước đ\u0026oacute; b\u0026agrave;y tỏ mong muốn gặp lại nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n “c\u0026oacute; thể ngay trong năm nay”, trong khi \u0026ocirc;ng Kim Jong Un hồi th\u0026aacute;ng trước cho biết vẫn “giữ những kỷ niệm tốt đẹp” về \u0026ocirc;ng Trump v\u0026agrave; sẵn s\u0026agrave;ng đối thoại nếu ph\u0026ugrave; hợp.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eC\u0026ugrave;ng ng\u0026agrave;y, Bộ trưởng Chung Dong Young nhấn mạnh Seoul “kh\u0026ocirc;ng muốn bỏ lỡ d\u0026ugrave; chỉ 1 phần trăm cơ hội” để th\u0026uacute;c đẩy đối thoại giữa hai b\u0026ecirc;n, đồng thời khẳng định H\u0026agrave;n Quốc sẵn s\u0026agrave;ng hỗ trợ nếu cuộc gặp được tổ chức.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLinh T\u0026ocirc; (TTXVN)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close (Esc)\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title\u003d\"Share\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title\u003d\"Toggle fullscreen\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title\u003d\"Zoom in/out\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__icn\"\u003e\n       \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__cut\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__donut\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n       \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__share-modal pswp__share-modal--hidd